{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "FUR/addparting", "parent": "guideprocess"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Part Guides"], "extent": [45, 61]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Lets you draw a parting line on the skin geometry."], "extent": [61, 120]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [120, 135], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool lets you draw a line on skin geometry, which stops any generated hair from being influenced by guide curves on the other side of the line. This is useful for getting a clean split along a line, for example where guides have already been groomed in opposite directions."], "extent": [135, 416]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Clicking ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "FUR/addparting", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/FUR/addparting"}, " ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Part Guides"]}, " on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Guide Process"]}, " tab will put down a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/hairclump", "type": "link", "text": ["Draw Curve SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/hairclump"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/guidepartition", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Partition SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/guidepartition"}, " where you can paint on the skin geometry. For more information, see the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/guidepartition", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Partition SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/guidepartition"}, " help page."], "extent": [416, 723]}]}], "title": ["Part Guides"], "summary": ["Lets you draw a parting line on the skin geometry."]}